snippet.title: Strategic Mind: Spirit of Liberty - Release Date Announcement
snippet.description:
The prologue of the fifth installment of the Strategic Mind series is now available. Check it out for FREE on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1683420/Strategic_Mind_Spirit_of_Liberty__Prologue_1939/

Spirit of Liberty will arrive on Steam 28th of August 2023 Wishlist & Follow to stay updated:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1474770/Strategic_Mind_Spirit_of_Liberty/

Strategic Mind: Spirit of Liberty is a history-driven turn-based strategy set in WW2. Lead the scarce Finnish forces through the Winter War, Continuation War, and Lapland War. Save your country’s very existence from the Red Menace. Niet Molotoff!

Twitter: https://twitter.com/HYPERSTRANGE
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/5tXPJY4
Strategic Mind: Spirit of Liberty (c) Starni Games
